#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Adds an option for users to mark comments as private, viewable only by "
"admins and the comment author."
msgstr "添加一个选项，让用户将评论标记为私人评论，只有管理员和评论作者才能查看。"

#: commentxpert.php:64
msgid "Allow site users to mark comments as private"
msgstr "允许网站用户将评论标记为私人评论"

#: commentxpert.php:139
msgid "Approve"
msgstr "批准"

#: commentxpert.php:221
msgid "Comment made private successfully."
msgstr "评论已成功设为私密。"

#: commentxpert.php:219
msgid "Comment made public successfully."
msgstr "评论公开成功。"

